Aïn Maabed

Aïn Maabed is a town and commune in Djelfa Province, Algeria. According to the 1998 census it has a population of 13,183.Aïn Maabed lies on the N1 Trans-Saharan highway to the north by road from the provincial capital of Djelfa.
